              <td align="left" valign="top" class="txt"><strong>POST-INTERVIEW MANNERS</strong><br />
                <br /> 	

once your interview is over comes the hardest part -- waiting for a response from the company. Use this interval in the most productive manner.<br />
<br /><ul>
                    <li>Always  write a note to the interviewer to thank them for their time.<strong> </strong><br />
                      <br />
                    </li>
                    <li>Without  gushing, reiterate your eagerness to work with the company.<strong> </strong><br />
                      <br />
                    </li>
                    <li>If  you have used any of your contacts as a reference, regardless of whether you  get the job or not, write to them also and thank them for their time and  effort.<strong> </strong><br />
                      <br />
                    </li>
